1. *Postojao* je jedan plan za izgradnju nove škole. (There was a plan for building a new school.)
2. Tokom godina, mnogo preduzeća je *postojalo* i propalo. (Over the years, many companies existed and failed.)
3. Ukoliko ne bi *postojao* ovaj zakon, situacija bi bila još gora. (If this law didn't exist, the situation would be even worse.)
4. Ona se trudila da *postoji* kao ozbiljan pisac. (She tried to establish herself as a serious writer.)
5. Mnoge vrste dinosaura više ne *postoje* danas. (Many types of dinosaurs no longer exist today.)
6. Kada sam poslednji put bio tamo, taj restoran je još uvek *postojao*. (The last time I was there, that restaurant was still in existence.)
7. Nadam se da će ta tradicija i dalje *postojati* u našoj porodici. (I hope that tradition will continue to exist in our family.)
8. Ako bismo *postojali* samo na ovom svetu, bilo bi nam dosadno. (If we existed only in this world, we would be bored.)
9. Čudno je kako neke stvari mogu *postojati* samo u našim glavama. (It's strange how some things can exist only in our minds.)
10. Pre nego što se udaljite, proverite da li vam dokumenti i dalje *postoje* u torbi. (Before you leave, check if your documents still exist in your bag.)